        <div1 type="body">
            


<p>Dear <persName>Son</persName></p>

<p>Inclosed you have Notices which I recd <date when="1818-07-23">yesterday</date></p>

<p>I have your Boat now in a Situation that when the river falls a
little she will be ready to under go any reparees you may wish to
make to hir&#8212;</p>

<p>You <persName>Mother </persName>and myself think of starting to the <placeName>mines </placeName>on Sunday
if we can</p>

<p>I am Respectfully Yours</p>

<p><persName>Moses Austin</persName></p>

<p><placeName>Herculanm   </placeName><date when="1818-07-24">July 24 1818</date></p>

<p>[Addressed:] <persName>Mr James Bryan</persName>   <placeName>Hazel Cottage</placeName></p>

        </div1>
